Braasch, 1990 B lamellae of gills 7 of 
<taxonomicName id="1A9C6B89F424C6022C692DE3A823D586" class="Insecta" family="Heptageniidae" genus="Epeorus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Epeorus khayengensis" order="Ephemeroptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="63" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="khayengensis">Epeorus khayengensis</taxonomicName>
Boonsoong &amp; Braasch, 2010 
<normalizedToken id="80DAF7AA9C026804E88E94FC5CFC2465" originalValue="C–E">C-E</normalizedToken>
ventral view of abdomen (C), abdominal gills 1 (D) and abdominal terga of (E) 
<taxonomicName id="997DF9E06236FA2438C7017F53336A6B" class="Insecta" family="Heptageniidae" genus="Epeorus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Epeorus thailandensis" order="Ephemeroptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="63" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="thailandensis">Epeorus thailandensis</taxonomicName>
sp. n. F abdominal terga of 
<taxonomicName id="1A5BAEF834A1BA1A9568BCD9EC18945E" class="Insecta" family="Heptageniidae" genus="Epeorus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Epeorus unicornutus" order="Ephemeroptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="63" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="unicornutus">Epeorus unicornutus</taxonomicName>
Braasch, 2006 G abdominal terga of 
<taxonomicName id="F7CF348250052309F5B3A36286C4DE90" class="Insecta" family="Heptageniidae" genus="Epeorus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Epeorus khayengensis" order="Ephemeroptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="63" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="khayengensis">Epeorus khayengensis</taxonomicName>
Boonsoong &amp; Braasch, 2010 
<normalizedToken id="3A16B9F418E836525251D7725A7D56FC" originalValue="H–J">H-J</normalizedToken>
abdominal terga (H), lamellae of gills 1 (I) and tergum VII (J) of 
<taxonomicName id="B682C879EC2B482CC444D50B05043C8C" class="Insecta" family="Heptageniidae" genus="Epeorus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Epeorus inthanonensis" order="Ephemeroptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="63" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="inthanonensis">Epeorus inthanonensis</taxonomicName>
Braasch &amp; Boonsoong, 2010.
</paragraph>
